HEADWORD: Mormon
<hw>Mor"mon</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr.
Gr. <grk>mormw`n</grk> monster, bugbear.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>A genus of sea birds, having a large, thick bill; the
